---
const year = 2026;
---
<footer class="border-t border-line mt-24 bg-ink text-paper">
  <div class="wrap py-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
    <div>
      <div class="font-display text-xl font-extrabold">ide<span class="text-spark">eea</span>s</div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-paper/70 max-w-xs">
        A growing library of validated startup and side-project ideas, demand, difficulty, money, and a starter stack for each.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-sm">
      <div class="font-semibold mb-3 text-paper/90">Explore</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-paper/70">
        <li><a href="/ideas/" class="hover:text-spark">All idea collections</a></li>
        <li><a href="/how-to-validate-a-startup-idea/" class="hover:text-spark">How to validate an idea</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-spark">About ideeeas</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="text-sm">
      <div class="font-semibold mb-3 text-paper/90">Get the weekly drop</div>
      <p class="text-paper/70 mb-3">10 validated ideas in your inbox every week.</p>
      <a href="/#subscribe" class="inline-block rounded-full bg-spark text-ink font-semibold px-4 py-2 hover:bg-paper transition-colors">Subscribe free</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wrap py-6 border-t border-paper/10 text-xs text-paper/50 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 justify-between">
    <span>© {year} ideeeas. Ideas are starting points, not guarantees, validate before you build.</span>
    <span>Some outbound tool links may be affiliate links.</span>
  </div>
</footer>
